{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/komikman-komik-terabsurd-2017/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Komikman, Komik Terabsurd 2017","content":"<p>Kalau ada penghargaan komik terabsurd, mungkin Komikman bisa jadi salah satu komik yang mengantongi nominasinya atau malah pemenangnya. Gimana enggak, komik yang ngakunya berisi konten <em>“18+ dark, receh, depressing, abnormal”</em> ini malah justru menjadi komik terabsurd 2017.</p>\n<p>Bercerita tentang seorang anak bernama D yang dikelilingi oleh kedua orang tuanya dan kedua kakak-kakaknya. Dia hidup menjadi anak yang sehat dan penuh kasih sayang bersama keluarganya. Komikman akan menggambarkan keseharian hidup dari D dan keluarga.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22716\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22716\" data-attachment-id=\"22716\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/komikman-komik-terabsurd-2017/attachment/isi-2-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-2-15.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Instagram: @komikman\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Instagram: @komikman&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-2-15.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-2-15.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22716\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-2-15.jpg\" alt=\"Instagram: @komikman\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-22716\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Instagram: @komikman</p></div></p>\n<p>Komik karya Dirga Deka ini berawal dari gambar-gambarnya yang sangat terkenal di media sosial Instagram. Dengan 67 ribu lebih <em>followers </em>di instagram, gak heran kalau Komikman dinobatkan menjadi salah satu <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/komik-strip-lucu-2017-kesukaan-kamu-yang-mana/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Komik Strip Lucu 2017 </strong></a>versi CIAYO Blog.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22713\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22713\" data-attachment-id=\"22713\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/komikman-komik-terabsurd-2017/attachment/isi-1-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-1-15.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Gambar Komikman di Instagram (Instagram: @komikman)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Gambar Komikman di Instagram (Instagram: @komikman)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-1-15.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-1-15.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22713\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-1-15.jpg\" alt=\"Gambar Komikman di Instagram (Instagram: @komikman)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-22713\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gambar Komikman di Instagram (Instagram: @komikman)</p></div></p>\n<p>Komikman ini sangat unik. Di saat komik lain berlomba-lomba menciptakan tokoh yang rupawan ataupun menonjol, Komikman menghadirkan tokoh yang sederhana namun mudah diingat. Bayangin aja, tokoh bulat menggemaskan layaknya hantu Casper. Walaupun jika diperhatikan lagi, semua tokoh berbentuk sama, tapi Dirga sang <em>author</em> menambahkan tulisan nama mereka di setiap jidat, sehingga membuat orang tidak bingung.</p>\n<p>Watak dari setiap tokoh pun diperlihatkan dengan jelas. Mulai dari D yang ceria namun sering kali tertindas, sang ibu yang pelupa, ayah yang baik tapi genit, sampai kedua kakaknya yang mata duitan dan perfeksionis. Gak akan membuat kita bosan buat membacanya.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-attachment-id=\"22719\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/komikman-komik-terabsurd-2017/attachment/isi-3-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-3-15.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-3-15.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-3-15.jpg\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-22719\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-3-15.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22722\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22722\" data-attachment-id=\"22722\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/komikman-komik-terabsurd-2017/attachment/isi-4-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-4-15.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-4-15.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-4-15.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22722\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-4-15.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-22722\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Komik bergenre <em>slice of life</em> ini juga dibumbui komedi, loh. Tapi bro sis harus menurunkan <em>sense of humor</em> dari level receh jadi jongkok kalau mau baca komik yang satu ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22725\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22725\" data-attachment-id=\"22725\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/komikman-komik-terabsurd-2017/attachment/isi-5-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-5-14.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-5-14.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-5-14.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22725\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-5-14.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-22725\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Berbeda dengan di Instagram, Komikman di CIAYO Comics hadir lebih ramah dengan judul <a href=\"https://ciayo.com/id/comic/komikman-an-ordinary-family-life\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Komikman: An Ordinary Family Life</a>. Gak percaya? Cek aja <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/komikman/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@komikman</a>.  Walaupun gambarnya terkesan lucu dan menggemaskan, tapi konsep ceritanya kebanyakan sadis. Darah di mana-mana. Udah kayak gambar di film <em>action</em>, deh.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_22728\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-22728\" data-attachment-id=\"22728\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/komikman-komik-terabsurd-2017/attachment/isi-6-14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-6-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Instagram: @komikman\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Instagram: @komikman&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-6-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-6-12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-22728\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-6-12.jpg\" alt=\"Instagram: @komikman\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-22728\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Instagram: @komikman</p></div></p>\n<p>Saat pertama kali baca, kita akan dibuat bingung sekaligus kesal bercampur aduk. Syukur-syukur langsung ngerti ceritanya. Buat yang masih bingung, harus membaca ulang kalau mau ngerti. Mau ketawa baca ini? Bisa kok. Tapi mesti jenius dulu kalau mau baca ini. Kalau masih bingung juga, kepoin aja <a href=\"https://ciayo.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics</a>. Psst, hati-hati nyesel, ya. Dijamin absurd pokoknya.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"24698bff-3ea0-55f6-a8b4-42826eefa609"}}}